headline: lululemon athletica inc. Announces Fourth Quarter and Full Year Fiscal 2024 Earnings Conference Call
summary: VANCOUVER, British Columbia, March 13, 2025--lululemon athletica inc. (NASDAQ: LULU) today announced that its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year fiscal 2024 will be released Thursday, March 27, 2025. The company will host a conference call at 4:30 p.m. Eastern time to discuss the financial results.
